➜都是手指，为什么中指就是那么与众不同
http://www.sohu.com/a/427825411_624188	12693
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201028/1993f20cb4fa49518602b020f74db5cb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世界上有70多亿人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人一多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">认识差异就产生了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就连手指</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也逃不过这样的命运</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为中国人的你可能永远不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为什么竖大拇指时会被揍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为什么在竖起食指和小拇指</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准备开始<strong>rock&amp;roll</strong>时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身边的人却开始哭了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201028/312d27d6a16945f79a858871db85a936.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">但在手指届</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有一只手指</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>却得到了全世界的认同</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201028/59f37d7df4d54bbba296376e24828193.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而要问<strong>竖中指</strong>这个国际手势的来源</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还得从<strong>英法</strong>之间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一场持续了百年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">名为<strong>百年战争</strong>的战争说起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/8003e47c3312488194849afdaf20e0c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早年间<strong>维京海盗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不在海上好好打工</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">反而老在法兰西<strong>诺曼底海岸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">左右横跳疯狂骚扰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至深入到内陆挑衅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为一国之王的<strong>查理三世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到此情此景表示——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201028/94d0886783674c358eb05a1bc4982d90.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在诺曼底定居的维京人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">非常的争气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把这块地是越搞越<strong>强大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西国王瞅着这发展趋势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">内心不禁慌了起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201028/bf5267bbe4434f7aab0f1fb75e1994a4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等法兰西国王意识到不对</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想入侵管控时 已经<strong>晚了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为诺曼底最强的大佬已经诞生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>威廉一世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他不仅让法兰西国王入侵计划失败</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">安稳统治着诺曼底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还顺带把英格兰也搞过来自己统治</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201028/60fda9db1ae449bf8e96a35717919edf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也把<strong>王室文化</strong>带去了英格兰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成了现代英国王室的开端</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那段时期的英国王室</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以说是非常<strong>牛哔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在英格兰和法兰西都有地盘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201028/75656af36c524919a4abc79f9c016378.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">威廉一世去世后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后代实在<strong>不给力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西趁机把诺曼底抢了回去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西终于可以弱受翻身变强攻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起身去搞英格兰？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201028/b461a2cd07fc4170b5b0b6816f2f2af3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为诺曼底被</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在法兰西出生的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由英格兰国王的<strong>女儿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和法兰西贵族生的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和法兰西国王路易七世有着亲戚关系的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后期还娶了路易七世老婆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至当上了英格兰国王的孩子——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>亨利二世</strong>继承了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/3be5eb21402949909b9fb12de400673e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亨利二世</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>既是法兰西的臣子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>又是英格兰的国王</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在英格兰至高无上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在法兰西却还得听国王的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人很不爽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/d7801e2968bc46d9b27e642c5bbfc7d3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果放弃法兰西身份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又得把搞到手的诺曼底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从父亲那继承的<strong>安茹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">娶了路易七世原配</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">带来的嫁妆<strong>阿基坦</strong>等地方让出去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就很亏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是亨利二世决定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>装</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>傻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>乖乖地承认法兰西国王的地位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>然后无视法他的一切命令</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201028/815f069bed6944739bad53e5ddb082db.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着亨利二世利用双重身份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坐拥两倍于自己的领土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让法兰西国王<strong>恨得牙痒痒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却又无可奈何</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只能将夺回法兰西领土的事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">交给后浪们来加油了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201028/67f1d56cad0f4b369c7715989061e82a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亨利二世开启的混乱关系</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>乱一代</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>代代乱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让英法后代关系越来越混乱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">互相都觉得自己能<strong>继承对方的皇位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把被拿走的地盘拿回来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主要就缺一个理由</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西国王</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>查理四世</strong>站了出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201028/906d943d7e8d482b8aebd3a35874a47a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西国王没儿子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而女性当时又没有继承权</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这接班人的位置</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就让英法两边都蠢蠢欲动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其中就有——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201028/07fdc0f415ed45b2baceab5e9ecc6fc1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然这么看上去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爱德华三世</strong>跟查理四世关系</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">离得更近点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/f1f902fba43746aa8f42d70dbac3d5a1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>法兰西三级会议</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早在20年前就规定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女性不能继承王位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再加上依据<strong>萨利克法典</strong>规定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母亲的血脉声明拥有继承权的男性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不得继承王位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱德华三世的继承合法性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就大大降低了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腓力继承了王位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>称腓力六世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201028/f19df4125ffc40b98916bcbf7a7dc14e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英格兰又拿出祖传的<strong>《圣经》</strong>说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">里面写了女子也有继承权</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱德华三世应该继承法兰西王位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是在众人的支持下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1337年11月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱德华三世带着军队</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出发去法兰西抢回王冠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>正式拉开了百年战争的帷幕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/a5388784c03945648d61dd62f042a974.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英法互殴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英格兰的胜算其实<strong>并不大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然亨利二世在世的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把法兰西好多土地搞到英格兰这边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过这么些年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西的后浪们非常努力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时刻不忘前人理想好好<strong>记仇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一点一点的夺回自家领土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201028/7307561d71f941b7943f57b4c2db17ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以在百年战争正式开启时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西有<strong>一千二百二十万多</strong>的人口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而英格兰只有<strong>勉强六百万</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还得跨海远征</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等跨到岸人都晕船凉一半了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还打个什么劲儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201028/1379571295e0422abfb5b48ab6a6a6c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出乎意料的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西士兵却被英格兰士兵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打得嗷嗷直叫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">节节败退</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腓力六世看了都<strong>直呼内行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201028/98a17862c8b6417c8ddea69194359509.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这其中的致胜小妙招就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>远程风筝打近战</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西<strong>骑兵</strong>很出名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">傻子才会去跟他们贴脸打</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以英格兰早就放弃了正面硬刚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">选择<strong>长弓兵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隔得老远就对着法军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">biubiubiu</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201028/2ae7c91c2d714e3c9633776b1d725132.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这致胜小妙招在<strong>克雷西战役</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被英格兰发挥得淋漓尽致：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这场战役中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法兰西派出了三万余人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">迎战英格兰的九千人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">差不多三倍人数的差距下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英格兰长弓手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接连射退了法军的15次冲锋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以<strong>法军伤亡万余人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>英军伤亡不到二百人</strong>的战绩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">取得了胜利</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/25ff0203d92d484291a0f0d29b39eb9a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一射就把法军射出心理阴影了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一看到长弓兵就想回家找妈妈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而英军这边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拉长弓需要用到的<strong>中指</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就成了他们<strong>炫耀的资本</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是每次开战前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英军就会<strong>竖起中指</strong>去挑衅法军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201028/8b9e984ac01242089111a7256227c592.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至在打赢之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还要向法兰西俘虏展示</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己优美的中指</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201028/79c71f5933ea40f4bd0f27b1c4eccab3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这样的操作下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>中指</strong>成为了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>挑衅和侮辱的代名词</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">得到全世界人民的认可（误）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在英国本地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实还附加了个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>反手比耶=F**K</strong>的意思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">原因是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">射箭时用了食指和中指</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201028/7d9194fd56824a37a2e83d8e6593a041.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于英法百年战争接下来发生了什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终的结局如何？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国就能这么无痛赢下战争吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果想看的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们下回接着再说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201028/4c1d9e6109c04fcab79d239a12bf7310.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
